### Register a normal user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "mysecretpassword",
  "role": "user"
}

###
### Register an admin
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin_jane",
  "email": "jane@admin.com",
  "password": "supersecure",
  "role": "admin"
}

###
### Register a moderator
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "moderator_bob",
  "email": "bob@moderator.com",
  "password": "moderatorpass",
  "role": "moderator"
}

###
### Login as normal user (Note: using form-urlencoded for OAuth2)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=johndoe&password=mysecretpassword

###
### Login as admin
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin_jane&password=supersecure

###
### Login as moderator
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=moderator_bob&password=moderatorpass

###
### Refresh Access Token (Copy refresh_token from login response)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###
### Get Current User (Copy the access_token from login and replace 'YOUR_TOKEN')
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###
### Try Moderator Route as Normal User (Should return 403 Forbidden)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/moderator-panel
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

###
### Access Moderator Panel as Moderator (Success - 200)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/moderator-panel
Authorization: Bearer MODERATOR_TOKEN

###
### Access Moderator Panel as Admin (Success - 200)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/moderator-panel
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###
### Try Admin Route as Normal User (Should return 403 Forbidden)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/admin-dashboard
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

###
### Try Admin Route as Moderator (Should return 403 Forbidden)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/admin-dashboard
Authorization: Bearer MODERATOR_TOKEN

###
### Access Admin Dashboard as Admin (Success - 200)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/admin-dashboard
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###
### Test Missing Token (Should return 401 Unauthorized)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/me

###
### Test Invalid Token (Should return 401 Unauthorized)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

###
### Test Wrong Password (Should return 401 Unauthorized)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=johndoe&password=wrongpassword

###
### Test Duplicate Username Registration (Should return 400 Bad Request)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "johndoe",
  "email": "another@example.com",
  "password": "anotherpass",
  "role": "user"
}